DFKI Head pose dataset
This dataset is composed of a video sequence with 1263 frames. 
It was recorded using an IR camera, while the groundtruth was acquired using an optical motion capture device.

Files:
This folder contains the following files:
*calib.txt: 		calibration data
*groudhtruth.txt: 	groundtruth data
*sequences:		1263 .png images

The groundtruth data is provided in the camera coordinate system, defined by the right-hand rule and with axes:
x: horizontal axis, oriented from left to right
y: vertical axis, pointing downwards
z: pointing inwards, parallel to the optical axis of the camera
The data is arranged as follows:
-Translation(in mm): From column 1 to column 3 [translation_x	translation_y	translation_z]
-Rotation: From column 4 to column 12 [rotMatrix_11	rotMatrix_21	rotMatrix_31	rotMatrix_12	rotMatrix_22	rotMatrix_32	rotMatrix_13	rotMatrix_23	rotMatrix_33]
rotation_Matrix = [rotMatrix_11	rotMatrix_12	rotMatrix_13;
		   rotMatrix_21	rotMatrix_22	rotMatrix_23;	
		   rotMatrix_31	rotMatrix_32	rotMatrix_33]

Citation:
This database is made available for research purposes only. In case of using the data provided here, please cite our work as follows:
@article{diazbarros2018real,
  title = {Real-Time Head Pose Estimation by Tracking and Detection of Keypoints and Facial Landmarks},
  author = {Diaz Barros, Jilliam Maria and Mirbach, Bruno and Garcia, Frederic and Varanasi, Kiran and Stricker, Didier},
  journal = {Communications in Computer and Information Science},
  year = {2018},
  publisher = {Springer}
}

